[EXHALES]

36:02.740 --> 36:04.420
But this was meant for you.

36:07.080 --> 36:11.340
Somehow Andrea's violin
found its way back to

36:11.350 --> 36:12.660
her heart

36:13.760 --> 36:15.100
where it belongs.

36:15.110 --> 36:22.499
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:22.500 --> 36:24.659
You said you don't know
how to move forward.

36:24.660 --> 36:27.340
Well, I think this is your way.

36:31.400 --> 36:34.279
I never did get to hear you play.

36:34.280 --> 36:36.100
Would you mind?

