[PLAYS MELANCHOLY MELODY]

36:41.490 --> 36:48.740
♪ ♪

36:49.240 --> 36:56.140
♪ ♪

36:56.480 --> 36:59.539
<i>[SOMBER MUSIC]</i>

36:59.540 --> 37:02.849
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:02.850 --> 37:04.909
I would first like to
thank the membership

37:04.910 --> 37:07.300
of St. Williams for having me.

37:07.380 --> 37:09.589
We've partnered in so many events

37:09.590 --> 37:12.490
over the years that it
feels like a second home.

37:15.100 --> 37:17.389
Thank you. Aw.

37:17.390 --> 37:19.129
Thank you so much for coming.

37:19.130 --> 37:20.340
- Of course.
- Do you want to sit?

37:20.360 --> 37:21.540
No, no, no.

37:21.550 --> 37:23.299
You said it was important
for us to be here.

37:23.300 --> 37:25.329
We just... we don't know why.

37:25.330 --> 37:28.480
I have a feeling your father
could use your support today.

37:28.540 --> 37:30.040
Investing in our community,

37:30.050 --> 37:32.480
making sure our children
have a safe place to learn,

37:32.500 --> 37:35.109
it's these core values that will ensure

37:35.110 --> 37:37.709
our future remains bright.

37:37.710 --> 37:38.879
Hm?

37:38.880 --> 37:40.620
[APPLAUSE]

37:40.630 --> 37:42.219
Please.

37:42.220 --> 37:43.889
Thank you, Reverend Finer.

37:43.890 --> 37:46.390
As you speak about core
values, I'm curious to hear

37:46.400 --> 37:49.689
your position on the LGBTQIA's
role in the church.

37:49.690 --> 37:52.820
Thank you for your question.
It's an important one.

37:52.880 --> 37:55.529
I think that everyone's relationship

37:55.530 --> 37:59.000
with God is different, that
when we're searching...

38:01.800 --> 38:04.660
I'm sorry, um...

38:05.300 --> 38:07.809
The answer I was about to give

38:07.810 --> 38:11.960
wasn't good enough for you or me.

38:13.940 --> 38:17.219
A few years ago, a parishioner of mine

38:17.220 --> 38:19.689
came to me to tell me
that they were gay.

38:19.690 --> 38:21.749
They were not struggling
with their sexuality

38:21.750 --> 38:24.289
or the decision to come out.

38:24.290 --> 38:29.969
They were struggling with
their place in the church.

38:29.970 --> 38:34.099
How they would be accepted
by the community.

38:34.100 --> 38:35.900
By me.

38:37.080 --> 38:40.110
I was shook by this.

38:41.180 --> 38:45.920
Because that parishioner...

38:47.880 --> 38:49.580
was my daughter.

38:50.750 --> 38:54.340
Through our journey, she
showed me the true meaning

38:54.350 --> 38:58.159
of courage, strength,

38:58.160 --> 38:59.760
of acceptance.

38:59.780 --> 39:03.300
I saw love in this.

39:03.370 --> 39:06.480
I saw God in this.

39:06.540 --> 39:09.299
<i>♪ This house speaks ♪</i>

39:09.300 --> 39:11.019
<i>[SOFT POP MUSIC]</i>

39:11.020 --> 39:14.780
<i>The heart is capable of
extraordinary things.</i>

39:14.800 --> 39:16.809
It gives us life,

39:16.810 --> 39:19.009
makes us feel love,

39:19.010 --> 39:21.719
and in some cases, can be passed on.

39:21.720 --> 39:24.089
<i>It's memories kept alive.</i>

39:24.090 --> 39:26.199
Thank you, Miles.

39:26.200 --> 39:28.289
Teaching Lindsay has
really helped Karen.

39:28.290 --> 39:30.429
I haven't seen my wife
smile in a very long time.

39:30.430 --> 39:32.160
<i>♪ When you get there ♪</i>

39:32.170 --> 39:36.320
<i>And of course the heart
is also full of mystery.</i>

39:36.350 --> 39:38.199
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:38.200 --> 39:40.480
<i>It can remind you of who you are.</i>

39:40.500 --> 39:44.139
What you said... it was beautiful.

39:44.140 --> 39:47.809
It wasn't what I expected to say.

39:47.810 --> 39:51.579
But it was what I needed to say.

39:51.580 --> 39:53.219
Mm-hmm.

39:53.220 --> 39:55.119
I'm also guessing that it was your idea

39:55.120 --> 39:57.649
to bring in Ali and Miles.

39:57.650 --> 40:00.259
I thought that you
could use the support.

40:00.260 --> 40:02.519
You know me so well.

40:02.520 --> 40:06.299
I also know that you should
always trust your heart

40:06.300 --> 40:08.419
because it will never steer you wrong.

40:08.420 --> 40:09.429
And you're right.

40:09.430 --> 40:12.299
I have been listening

40:12.300 --> 40:15.640
to my heart for some time now.

40:17.060 --> 40:19.540
And it's telling me that I love you.

40:20.680 --> 40:22.780
I love you too.

40:22.800 --> 40:24.810
[BOTH CHUCKLE]

40:26.080 --> 40:29.079
<i>Or tear you in two directions.</i>

40:29.080 --> 40:30.939
What do you think? Is Simon Hayes behind

40:30.940 --> 40:32.840
- the God Account?
- I think so.

40:32.850 --> 40:35.089
And I think he's going to reveal that

40:35.090 --> 40:37.199
to the world next week at his gala.

40:37.200 --> 40:39.829
He offered me an exclusive if I hold off

40:39.830 --> 40:41.329
from publishing until afterward.

40:41.330 --> 40:43.780
Afterwards? It's no longer an exclusive.

40:44.860 --> 40:46.520
Do you have enough to start writing?

40:46.540 --> 40:48.299
Yeah?

40:48.300 --> 40:50.940
Then I want to publish
it before the gala.

40:53.160 --> 40:57.599
<i>And, sure, along the
way the heart is bound</i>

40:57.600 --> 41:00.160
to pick up scars,

41:00.170 --> 41:03.260
painful reminders of the past.

41:03.280 --> 41:06.319
But if you trust it,

41:06.320 --> 41:08.340
follow it where it wants you to go,

41:08.350 --> 41:10.960
it will always lead you
in the right direction.

41:10.980 --> 41:15.629
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:15.630 --> 41:17.240
- Hey.
- Hey, hey.

41:17.250 --> 41:19.499
What's going on? You wanted to see me?

41:19.500 --> 41:21.569
Yeah.

41:21.570 --> 41:23.509
There's just something I
wanted to talk to you about.

41:23.510 --> 41:26.379
[LAUGHS] Okay. So what's up?

41:26.380 --> 41:28.979
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:28.980 --> 41:31.549
When we were here a couple of days ago,

41:31.550 --> 41:34.649
you asked me to reconsider
writing the story

41:34.650 --> 41:36.760
- for my boss.
- Mm-hmm.

41:36.900 --> 41:39.149
I did.

41:39.150 --> 41:41.989
That's great. Okay, what's it about?

41:41.990 --> 41:43.729
<i>♪ When you ♪</i>

41:43.730 --> 41:45.389
Simon Hayes.

41:45.390 --> 41:48.059
<i>♪ I'll tell you everything ♪</i>

41:48.060 --> 41:49.499
You mean the God Account?

41:49.500 --> 41:51.629
Yeah.

41:51.630 --> 41:54.469
But I... I came to you

41:54.470 --> 41:56.219
when FreeVerse told me that they wanted

41:56.220 --> 41:58.339
exclusive rights for the God Account.

41:58.340 --> 42:00.499
You looked me in my eyes and told me

42:00.500 --> 42:01.860
that it was not a problem,
that you weren't gonna

42:01.880 --> 42:03.480
- write an article about it.
- Yeah, I know.

42:03.500 --> 42:05.679
You stood right there

42:05.680 --> 42:07.100
and told me how proud you were,

42:07.110 --> 42:09.349
how great of an opportunity this is.

42:09.350 --> 42:10.640
You don't understand, okay?

42:10.650 --> 42:13.819
Someone at "Catapult" was
going to write the article.

42:13.820 --> 42:18.280
- What was I supposed to say?
- You were supposed to say no.

42:19.740 --> 42:23.569
Cara, this is not your story to tell.

42:23.570 --> 42:25.629
Miles...

42:25.630 --> 42:28.169
the God Account isn't just yours.

42:28.170 --> 42:30.239
It's all of ours.

42:30.240 --> 42:32.009
But we had a deal.

42:32.010 --> 42:33.939
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:33.940 --> 42:36.709
Well, I'm sorry.

42:36.710 --> 42:38.749
Things changed.

42:38.750 --> 42:42.300
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:42.320 --> 42:44.959
Yeah, I guess they have.

